@wp.kernel
def expr_vskinm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(v1))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp((v2 + 0.63 / v0 + 0.06)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = wp.abs((v0 - (tmp + 0.95 / v2 + 0.02)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
